c: 11
v: 31
t: "“Simbabwira ko mfite ibigega bya Allah, nta n’ubwo nzi ibitagaragara, ndetse nta n’ubwo mbabwira ko ndi umumalayika, kandi nta n’ubwo mbwira abo amaso yanyu asuzugura ko Allah atazabahundagazaho ibyiza. Allah ni We uzi ibiri mu mitima yabo. (Ndamutse mbibabwiye) naba mbaye mu nkozi z’ibibi.”"